\s UHORAHO NIWE MUKIZA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Uhoraho niwe \bd*\bd Mukiza\bd*\bd , Uhoraho niwe mwungere, anvyagiza mu canya c’ubwatsi butotahaye, antegurira imeza imbere y’abansi banje.\bd*
\pc \bdit Niwe \bdit*\bdit Mwungere Aruta \bdit*\bdit abungere, niwe \bdit*\bdit Mukunzi Aruta \bdit*\bdit abakunzi,\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit uwageze mu \bdit*\bdit Biganza \bdit*\bdit vyiwe, nta \bdit*\bdit Mwansi \bdit*\bdit yomukorako\bdit*\bd .\bd*
\zoli1 \bd Nta mwana w’Imana ashobora kumaramara, kukw’Uhoraho nyen’inkomezi, ashobora kumuzigama, naho yoba mu magorwa akomeye, afise intsinzi.\bd*
\pc \bdit Niwe Mwungere Aruta abungere, niwe Mukunzi Aruta abakunzi,\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit uwageze mu Biganza vyiwe, nta Mwansi yomukorako\bdit*\bd .\bd*
\zoli1 \bd Imana ishimwe, ku ntambwe zose twaciyemwo, ibikomeye twarabinesheje ibigatanya tubirya butsinda, ibitur’imbere, tuzobitsinda mw’izina ry’Umwami wacu.\bd*
